DEFINE VAR __SQDS0Core = 
	FILTER(
		KEEPFILTERS(
			SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
				'calendar'[date],
				"Mindate", CALCULATE(MIN('calendar'[date])),
				"Maxdate", CALCULATE(MAX('calendar'[date])),
				"Mwh", IGNORE('calendar'[Mwh])
			)
		),
		NOT(ISBLANK([Mwh]))
	)

EVALUATE
	SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
		__SQDS0Core,
		"Mindate", IGNORE(CALCULATE(MIN('calendar'[date]))),
		"Maxdate", IGNORE(CALCULATE(MAX('calendar'[date])))
	)

DEFINE VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
	FILTER(
		KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('calendar'[date])),
		'calendar'[date] >= DATE(2022, 2, 17)
	)

EVALUATE
	SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(__DS0FilterTable, "refresh_time", IGNORE('calendar'[refresh_time]))

DEFINE

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		FILTER(
			KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('calendar'[date])),
			'calendar'[date] >= DATE(2022, 2, 17)
		)

	VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
		TREATAS({"Black coal"}, 'duid'[FuelSourceDescriptor])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'calendar'[date],
			'duid'[State],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			__DS0FilterTable2,
			"Mwh", 'calendar'[Mwh]
		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0PrimaryDbCount = 
		CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'calendar'[date])))

	VAR __DS0SecondaryDbCount = 
		CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'duid'[State])))

	VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
		SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(3500, __DS0Core, 'calendar'[date], [Mwh], 350, 'duid'[State], ALPHABETICAL, ASC, 105000, 60)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0BodyBinnedSample, 'duid'[State])

	VAR __DS0SecondaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0SecondaryBase))

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
			__DS0BodyBinnedSample,
			"ColumnIndex",
			__DS0SecondaryBase,
			'duid'[State],
			ASC
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount,
		"DS0PrimaryDbCount", __DS0PrimaryDbCount,
		"DS0SecondaryDbCount", __DS0SecondaryDbCount,
		"DS0SecondaryCount", __DS0SecondaryCount
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0SecondaryBase

ORDER BY
	'duid'[State]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'calendar'[date], [ColumnIndex]
